        advanced: 'Apply cottagecore aesthetic celebrating romanticized rural simplicity. Color palette: soft, muted naturals - sage green (#9caf88), dusty rose (#d4a5a5), cream (#fffef0), lavender (#e6e6fa), warm brown (#8b7355), butter yellow (#f5deb3). Floral elements: wildflower illustrations, pressed flower collages, botanical drawings, flower borders (SVG). Patterns: gingham check (CSS repeating gradient), toile de Jouy pastoral scenes, delicate floral prints, lace borders. Textures: linen fabric weave, embroidery stitch patterns, aged paper, woven baskets. Typography: handwritten scripts (Dancing Script, Great Vibes), vintage serifs (Libre Baskerville), hand-lettering style. Imagery: cottage illustrations, garden scenes, baking and preserving, mushrooms, bees, herbs. Decorative elements: mason jars, vintage keys, dried flowers, ribbons, wax seals. Photography style: soft focus, golden hour lighting, film grain, slightly desaturated. Frame elements: scalloped edges, embroidery hoop shapes, botanical frames. Interactive: gentle hover effects, soft transitions, nothing jarring. Seasonal: spring/summer flowers, autumn harvest, cozy winter touches. Modern mix: combine vintage elements with clean layouts for usability. Accessibility: script fonts can be hard to read - use sparingly for headings, ensure decorative elements dont obscure content.'
