        advanced: 'Apply Notion/Linear aesthetic with modern productivity patterns. Background: bg-white with subtle bg-gray-50 sections. Borders: border-gray-200, use sparingly, prefer spacing over lines. Typography: Inter or similar sans-serif, tight tracking, clear hierarchy (text-2xl font-semibold for titles, text-sm text-gray-500 for meta). Icons: consistent 20px Lucide/Heroicons, stroke-width 1.5. Buttons: minimal - text buttons with hover:bg-gray-100, primary actions with bg-gray-900 text-white. Input fields: border-0 with bg-gray-100, focus:ring-0 focus:bg-gray-200. Keyboard hints: kbd styling with bg-gray-100 border rounded px-1.5 text-xs. Lists: hover:bg-gray-50, selected:bg-blue-50. Inline editing: click-to-edit with seamless transition, no modal. Sidebar: w-60, collapsible, section headers text-xs uppercase text-gray-500, items with icons. Tables: minimal headers, row hover, inline actions. Command palette: Cmd+K, clean search with grouped results. Animations: subtle, fast (150ms), no bounce. Drag handles: appear on hover, 6-dot grip. Empty states: centered, minimal illustration, action button.'
