        advanced: 'Apply Vercel aesthetic with developer platform patterns. Background: bg-black or bg-[#0a0a0a], sections with bg-[#111]. Text: text-white for primary, text-gray-400 for secondary. Gradient text: bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-gray-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent. Borders: border-[#333] thin, cards with border hover:border-gray-600. Code blocks: bg-[#1a1a1a] with bright syntax highlighting, filename tabs. Orbs: fixed gradient circles with blur-3xl, animate-pulse subtle. Grid patterns: repeating grid lines as background SVG or gradient. Buttons: bg-white text-black for primary, border border-gray-700 for secondary. Inputs: bg-transparent border-gray-700, focus:border-white. Monospace: font-mono for numbers, stats, code. Metrics: large text-5xl font-bold numbers with unit text-sm. Cards: bg-[#111] border border-gray-800, hover glow effect. Navigation: minimal, logo left, links center/right. Footer: comprehensive with multiple columns. Animations: smooth, purposeful, no excess. Deployment status: green/yellow/red dots with status text.'
