        advanced: 'Apply Spotify aesthetic with music app patterns. Background: bg-[#121212], gradients extracted from album art at top. Sidebar: bg-[#000] w-56, logo top, nav links, playlists list, resize handle. Content: scrollable, gradient header fading to bg. Album art: rounded-md shadows, hover shows play button overlay. Play button: rounded-full bg-green-500, centered play icon, hover:scale-105. Cards: album/playlist cards with image, title, subtitle, hover darken overlay. Carousels: horizontal scroll with arrow buttons on hover, snap to item. Track list: table with #, title (with explicit badge), album, date added, duration, hover shows more actions. Now playing bar: fixed bottom, album art small, track info, controls center, volume/queue right. Progress bar: thin green line, hover expands, draggable. Lyrics: synced highlight scroll, black overlay on album art background. Queue: slide-in panel from right. Search: large input, recent searches, browse categories grid. Explicit badge: text-[10px] border border-gray-400 rounded px-1. Context menus: dark themed, comprehensive options. Animations: smooth page transitions, play button bounce.'
