        advanced: 'Apply Discord aesthetic with chat platform patterns. Background: bg-[#313338] for main, bg-[#2b2d31] for sidebars. Server bar: w-18, circular icons with unread indicator, selected with pill left. Channel sidebar: w-60, category headers (collapsible), channel rows with icons (#, speaker, etc), selected bg-[#404249]. Messages: flex with avatar left, username (role color), timestamp on hover, message content, reactions below. Message input: bottom, textarea with formatting buttons, emoji picker, file attach. Embeds: max-w-lg, left color border, rich preview (images, links, code). Reactions: emoji pills with count, add reaction +. Mentions: bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400, @role, @user, #channel. Threads: reply count badge, side panel for thread view. Voice channels: user avatars when connected, mute/deafen icons. User sidebar: grouped by role, status indicator dot. Status: online (green), idle (yellow), dnd (red), offline (gray). User popup: profile card on click, roles, mutual servers. Roles: colored dots/names, role management. Search: messages, users, filter by date/channel. Notifications: badge counts, ping sounds. Streaming: Go Live indicator.'
