        advanced: 'Apply Airbnb aesthetic with booking platform patterns. Colors: white bg, text-gray-900, accent #FF385C (Airbnb pink) for CTAs. Search bar: prominent, location input, date range picker, guest counter, search button. Photos: aspect-square carousel with dots, fill cover, rounded-xl. Listing cards: image carousel, heart overlay top-right, title, rating, price per night. Map: split view or full screen, custom markers with price, cluster at zoom out. Filters: horizontal pill row, modal for more filters, clear all option. Date picker: inline calendar, range selection, blocked dates grayed. Reviews: star rating, review count, individual reviews with avatar. Host section: circular avatar, superhost badge, response rate. Booking widget: sticky sidebar, price breakdown, reserve button, rare find badge. Amenities: icon grid with labels. Location: map with approximate area circle. House rules: icons with descriptions. Cancellation: policy summary with link. Wishlist: filled heart, save to list modal. Mobile: bottom bar for booking, swipe photos. Trust: verified badges, ID confirmation. Footer: comprehensive links, language/currency selectors.'
