        advanced: 'Apply TikTok aesthetic with short-video patterns. Video container: full viewport height, swipe-up transitions, snap scrolling. Video: object-cover, tap to pause, double-tap to like (heart animation). Right sidebar: like button (heart) with count, comment bubble, bookmark, share arrow, creator avatar with follow plus. Bottom overlay: @username, description with hashtags (linked), sound marquee. Sound: music note icon, spinning album art, tap to view sound page. Progress bar: thin line at bottom showing video progress. Discover: grid of thumbnails, trending tags, search bar. Profile: header with stats (following, followers, likes), bio, grid of videos. Effects: filter browser, AR effects preview. Following/For You: tab switch at top. Comments: bottom sheet, sorted by likes, reply threading. Live: red Live badge, viewer count, gift animations. Create: camera with effects, timer, speed, flip camera. Notifications: activity feed with thumbnails. Accessibility: auto-captions, text-to-speech. Sounds: waveform visualization, favorites. Responsive: desktop shows multiple columns, mobile is primary.'
