        advanced: 'Apply Slack aesthetic with team communication patterns. Workspace switcher: vertical icon bar, notifications badge, add workspace. Sidebar: workspace name header, sections (Channels, Direct Messages, Apps), channel/DM rows with unread bold and count. Message area: date separators, messages with avatar, name, timestamp, content. Threading: click to open thread in right panel, reply count on parent. Message actions: emoji reaction, reply, more (edit, delete, pin, bookmark). Rich formatting: markdown, code blocks, blockquotes, lists. Emoji: picker with categories, search, recent, custom emoji. Reactions: row of emoji with counts below message. Files: upload, preview thumbnails, expand to viewer. @mentions: blue text, mention picker on @. Channels: # prefix, topic below name, members count. DMs: avatar, online status dot. Presence: green (active), empty (away), dnd (red). Search: top bar, filters (in:channel, from:person, has:link). Pins: pinned items list in channel details. Integrations: bot messages with app icon. Huddle: audio call in channel with participants shown. Bookmarks: toolbar below channel header. Settings: notifications per channel.'
